.copy If art is not your jam, just go and walk around in there, just for the architecture alone. Take some photos (they allow photography) and post to Instagram. People will think you’re cool.<br /><br /> If you plan to visit, make reservations online to avoid long wait times. The infinite room has an especially long line because space is limited.
